            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐洲央行執委Cipollone稱全球動盪可能影響歐元區復甦",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據西班牙《國家報》報導，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:歐洲央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐洲央行\">歐洲央行</a>執委Piero Cipollone在接受該報採訪時警告，全球動盪可能衝擊歐元區。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「不確定性可能會加劇，進而影響經濟復甦的力度，因為它會危及投資，」他對該報表示。「這可能會產生影響，尤其對經濟成長而言，顯然也會影響通膨。若這種不確定性持續存在，將對實體經濟造成衝擊。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲央行自去年6月以來一直沒有降息，鑒於通膨率徘徊在2%的目標附近，投資者和大多數經濟學家預計該行將在整個2026年按兵不動。歐洲央行最新預測顯示，今年歐元區經濟料成長1.2%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f0b7e4e4-a445-31b7-b362-2e548d1b8459-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「GDP表現穩健，我們預計實際數據甚至可能優於預期，」 Cipollone表示。「近幾個月來，通膨率一直在我們的目標水平附近波動。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Cipollone負責歐洲央行的數字歐元項目，他重申了這項工作的重要性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「潛在的地緣政治緊張局勢以及任何支付工具的軍事化都會增加風險，這更加凸顯了我們需要一個能夠滿足我們所有支付需求、基於歐洲技術和基礎設施的歐洲支付系統，」他說。「也就是說，一個完全由我們掌控的系統。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題ECB’s Cipollone Says Uncertainty May Increase, Hitting Recovery</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%9F%B7%E5%A7%94cipollone%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%AA%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E5%8D%80%E5%BE%A9%E7%94%A6-061410505.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 14:48:22",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "軟銀據悉正在商談向OpenAI追加投資不超過300億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:軟銀;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/軟銀\">軟銀</a>集團正在商討向OpenAI追加投資不超過300億美元，顯示創始人孫正義希望在人工智能發展中扮演核心角色的雄心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">軟銀已是OpenAI的最大投資者之一。因討論未公開信息而要求匿名的知情人士稱，軟銀還在考慮向這家快速成長的人工智能公司追加投資。其中一位知情人士稱，軟銀正在考慮的最高投資額為300億美元，討論仍在進行中，投資規模可能會變化。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">受此消息提振，軟銀股價一度飆升8.8%，隨後收窄漲幅，周三東京午後交易時段上漲約 3.7%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7ef77390-eea1-30eb-acff-d594ad065599-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為提高軟銀在OpenAI的持股比例，並為一項旨在把人工智能注入所有設備的大規模投資備足資金，孫正義近期一直在調整資產配置。軟銀已出售所持輝達股份，並且最近暫停收購美國數據中心運營商Switch的談判。軟銀已累計持有OpenAI約11%的股份，並在上月剛投資了225億美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">軟銀代表拒絕就這筆潛在投資置評。《華爾街日報》此前率先報導了這一消息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題SoftBank Is in Talks to Invest $30 Billion More in OpenAI (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Alice French、Natasha Mascarenhas、Min-Jeong Lee、Jillian Ward、Vlad Savov.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BB%9F%E9%8A%80%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%95%86%E8%AB%87%E5%90%91openai%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%85%E9%81%8E300%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-042528393.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 12:59:40",
