        },
        {
            "title": "中國以電力建設浪潮支持產業升級 四年新增裝機超過全美國電力容量",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"National Energy Administration; BloombergNEF\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"756\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tP0IfMCNoXd_yrYBN2URHw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc1Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/08d53edb9c8243452772a8d480008c33\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">National Energy Administration; BloombergNEF</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國正在掀起一場全球罕見的能源擴建浪潮，全力保障關鍵高能耗設施的用電需求，而這些設施對於中國主宰未來的新興產業至關重要。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據國家能源局周三公佈的數據，去年中國新增各類發電裝機容量543吉瓦。這一規模比印度截至2024年底所有電廠的總裝機容量還要多出12%。中國自2021年底以來新增的發電裝機規模，也超過了整個美國電力系統的容量。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"756\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UlBhbwfOdKtqHr2gCRcD4A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc1Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/aad0d0bec500aedac7694d3a9092369c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國國家主席習近平的目標，是確保能源供應穩定充裕，減少對進口燃料的依賴，並為人工智能、機器人製造和先進材料等快速成長且能源需求旺盛的產業提供競爭優勢。與此同時，外界日益擔心這些產業在美國的發展可能因缺乏廉價電力而受到掣肘。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a85e5653-3b7b-3ae8-b836-7deac917c0db-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「能源建設的推進力度依然非常強勁，各項數據都不斷刷新紀錄，」牛津能源研究所中國能源研究負責人Michal Meidan表示，「首要任務是保障能源供應安全，不僅如此，還要確保能源價格具有競爭力。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「能源必須服務於產業創新、工業升級和技術進步——這是中國‘十五五’規劃中經濟政策的核心，」Meidan說道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相比之下，美國的電力需求似乎在數十年前已進入平台期，此後新增發電裝機速度明顯較慢。高盛集團全球大宗商品研究聯席主管Samantha Dart指出，隨著人工智能的快速發展，美國正竭力滿足數據中心等高耗能行業的用電需求，導致電力市場處於供應極為緊張的狀態。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「美國可能會面臨瓶頸，而中國似乎完全沒有遇到類似限制，」她說道，「美國目前在人工智能競賽中居於領導地位，但隨著時間推移，中國可能將逐步占據上風。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Four-Year Energy Spree Has Eclipsed Entire US Power Grid</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BB%A5%E9%9B%BB%E5%8A%9B%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E6%B5%AA%E6%BD%AE%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%94%A2%E6%A5%AD%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E8%A3%9D%E6%A9%9F%E8%B6%85%E9%81%8E%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%8A%9B%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F-080830669.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 17:09:46",
