            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "高盛警告基本金屬漲勢面臨風險 終端需求已出現消極反應",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 高盛集團表示，基本金屬年初以來的漲勢將遭遇逆風，因為價格大幅飆升及市場看漲情緒，背離了製造業需求趨於疲軟的現實，這一點在中國市場尤為明顯。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「真正在一線的生產企業開始作出負面反應，」高盛股票研究聯席主管Trina Chen在接受彭博電視台採訪時表示，「我們看到需求有所回落。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2026年初幾周，從銅到鋁等多種金屬價格持續攀升，全球投資者紛紛湧入工業金屬市場，押注供應趨緊、美元走軟以及聯儲會降息。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4c42da69-428b-3f13-9442-81648ecb1923-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Trina Chen指出，高盛最近對銅市場所做的調查顯示，由於從消費電子到五金等行業的用戶減少採購，金屬加工企業的訂單量已下降10%至30%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「就連電網訂單也在放緩，」她說道。在亞洲最大經濟體中國，來自電網領域的需求是銅消費主力軍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">涵蓋倫敦金屬交易所六大金屬的LMEX金屬指數今年迄今上漲約7%，距離2022年觸及的歷史高點僅一步之遙。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Goldman Warns Metal Rally at Risk as Users ‘Respond Negatively’</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E9%87%91%E5%B1%AC%E6%BC%B2%E5%8B%A2%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E7%B5%82%E7%AB%AF%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E5%B7%B2%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E6%B6%88%E6%A5%B5%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89-064545556.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 15:39:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "加密貨幣巨頭悄然囤貨 CEO豪言Tether將成全球最大黃金央行之一",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Tether\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"716\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XhTNILP0LnP.f7gY7RmpcQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxNg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/02a1e13226743672684752299587b3fd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Tether</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 瑞士有大約37萬個冷戰時期遺留下來的核掩體，現在很少使用。然而，其中有一個當前異常活躍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">每周都有超過一噸黃金運入加密貨幣巨頭Tether Holdings SA擁有的這個戒備森嚴的金庫，它是目前已知的全球最大非銀行、非國家黃金倉庫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在過去一年裡，Tether悄然成為全球黃金市場最大參與者之一 —— 這是加密貨幣和黃金世界相遇的體現，這兩個世界都不信任政府債務，是金價飆升至歷史新高的一大原因。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-00821e15-475b-307e-a4f1-b7b855935ce1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而，其內部運作，或者說黃金策略，卻很少為外界所知。去年，當兩位資深黃金交易員從黃金業務大行滙豐控股離職時，業內熱議他們要去哪裡；但很少有人猜到答案是Tether。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在接受彭博新聞社採訪時，執行長Paolo Ardoino將該公司在黃金市場中的角色與央行相提並論，並預測華盛頓的地緣政治對手將會推出由黃金支持的美元替代品。他還透露，該公司計畫繼續將巨額利潤投入黃金市場，同時開始與銀行在黃金交易領域展開競爭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他說：「這麼說吧，我們基本上很快就會成為世界上最大的黃金央行之一。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Paolo Ardoino攝影師：Suhaimi Abdullah/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pE0wrP4Tuv3rKsZVY0FuGw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f5fa39606c0ea24fb8ca88d3d6be7e90\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Paolo Ardoino攝影師：Suhaimi Abdullah/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金市場眼下處在一個歷史性時期，但就算是在這樣一個背景下，Tether的動作也顯得格外之大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博計算，該公司迅速加大了購買力度，在去年一年裡買入超過70噸黃金，用於囤積和支持自己的黃金穩定幣。這一數字幾乎超過了任何一家央行公佈的購買量：只有波蘭宣布的增持量（102噸）比它高。此外超過它的就只有三大交易所交易基金(ETF)的購買量了，而後者代表了成千上萬的個人交易者和投資者的集體行動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據Ardoino稱，該公司持有約140噸黃金。這些黃金現在價值約230億美元，是在央行、ETF和商業銀行之外的已知最大庫藏。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">而且這個數字未來只會越來越高：Ardoino表示，Tether一直都以每周一到兩噸的步伐買入，並打算「在接下來的幾個月裡肯定要」繼續這樣做。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「當然，我們會根據市場情況做出決定，但我認為我們會沿著這條路走下去，」這位41歲的義大利人補充道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當被問及Tether會否在某個時候減少購買時，Ardoino表示：「也許我們會減少，現在還不知道。我們將逐季評估我們對黃金的需求。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"716\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/10PkLgObr7uvD5e5SA_pCQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxNg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/aa26af8452442fc73a523b4dca9df81f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Tether Is Shaking Up the Gold Market With Massive Metal Hoard</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Archie Hunter、Sybilla Gross.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD%E6%82%84%E7%84%B6%E5%9B%A4%E8%B2%A8-ceo%E8%B1%AA%E8%A8%80tether%E5%B0%87%E6%88%90%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E4%B9%8B-063740982.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 15:18:09",
